From 7c2e0752df1833808ed496a865f3f13b75ef150d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pat Whelan <pat.whelan@elastic.co>
Date: Mon, 14 Oct 2024 12:45:56 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] [ML] Ignore unrecognized openai sse fields (#114715)

Azure / Llama sends back fields we do not expect - rewriting the parser
to better handle unknown fields (by dropping them).
